  "prompt": "When will Quora support Arabic language?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, Quora has not officially announced a timeline for full Arabic language support. The platform has been gradually expanding its language offerings, but it hasn't included Arabic yet. Quora's decision to support a new language typically depends on user demand, community growth, and technical feasibility.\n\nIf you're interested in seeing Arabic support on Quora, you can:\n\n1. **Provide Feedback**: Let Quora know through their feedback channels that you'd like Arabic support.\n2. **Engage with Existing Communities**: Participate in Arabic-related discussions on Quora in English or other languages to show demand.\n3. **Stay Updated**: Keep an eye on Quora's announcements or blog for any updates on new language support.\n\nFor the most current information, check Quora's official communications or their help center.",
